3. NO REBRANDING, NO REPACKAGING AS ORIGINAL WORK (REQUIRED)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
You may NOT:

  a. Redistribute the Software — or any substantially similar derivative —
     under a different addon name while presenting it as original work.
